{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setdragstate:animated:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setDragState:animated:"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the current drag state for the annotation view."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDragState:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState","preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@MLNAnnotationViewDragState","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationViewDragState"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dragState","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can override this method to animate a custom annotation view as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"drags it. As the system detects user actions that would indicate a drag, it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calls this method to update the drag state."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setDragState:animated:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"setDragState:animated:","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L279"},"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationViewDragState":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationviewdragstate","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationViewDragState","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"These constants indicate the current drag state of an annotation view."}],"title":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setDragState:animated:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setDragState:animated:"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setDragState:animated:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setDragState:animated:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setdragstate:animated:","title":"setDragState:animated:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the current drag state for the annotation view."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic"}}}